				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I'm looking for some gear suggestions.
<br />

<br />
I'm coming back to my mage after taking a break for almost a year.  I'm currently unguilded, I have planar access up to Tactics, I have all expansions except GoD, and I am flat broke.
<br />

<br />
Clearly, obtaining more of the MMC high end gear is one way I can get some upgrades, but I wanted to see if anyone had suggestions on other items that I might be able to obtain with a group of friends (i.e. not a guild).
<br />

<br />
(I should also note that obtaining the Earring of the Solstice is the next thing I'm going to do once I can scrape together a few K).
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=866528" target="_blank" class="postlink">My Magelo</a>
<br />

<br />
