				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Here is my 2cp worth.
<br />

<br />
Belt: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=43417" target="_blank" class="postlink">Buckled Shale Belt</a> or if you can raise the funds <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=15883" target="_blank" class="postlink">Girdle of Mithaniel</a>
<br />

<br />
Arms: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=11597" target="_blank" class="postlink">ORANTE</a> .... well as soon as possible the Mana Pres is worth it IMO.
<br />

<br />
Head: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=9908" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ornate</a>,  the pattern isnt that expensive (2-5kish on Emarr anyway).
<br />

<br />
Gloves: aim for ... you guessed it, <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=13618" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ornate!</a>
<br />

<br />
Secondary: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=27284" target="_blank" class="postlink">Tactician's Bulwark</a>, again IMO the best caster shield in the bazaar atm (and as low as 6k on emarr).
<br />

<br />
Back: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=68391" target="_blank" class="postlink">Polychromatic Pelerine</a>, more like just another option then an upgrade.
<br />

<br />
Rings: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=62021" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ring of Depravity</a> and <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=21495" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ring of Thunderous Spirits</a> are also good.
<br />

<br />
Lastly bracer: <a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=11017" target="_blank" class="postlink">Wristband of Strategy</a> or anything with saves and HP on it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=692660" target="_blank" class="postlink">Vyaniu Vivisection</a>
<br />
65 Arch Convoker
<br />
Erollisi Marr
<br />
