				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If you have done or can get VP access, go crazy and start doing those.  Really really nice items.  Once you have the key, the majority of the quests are one groupable.
<br />

<br />
most of the quest can be found in the Quests of Norrath at <a href="http://www.safehouse.org" target="_blank">www.safehouse.org</a>
<br />

<br />
Ring of the Silver Dragon- Silverwing Quest
<br />
<a href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=69382" target="_blank">http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=69382</a>
<br />

<br />
Amice of the Skywings-  Druushk Quest
