			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I see you have been in CoN to kill Innoruuk.  A big upgrade to your Gnoll ring would be the FT 2 ring (Hate Forged Ring) he drops.
<br />

<br />
Those of you who haven't been there he's a pain in the @ss.  Gotta be in melee range or he resists everything, AE knockback/debuff every 35 seconds or so, Luggald Broodmother is right in the way to Inni so you either need to keep him mezzed or charmed or deal with her, and the least of your worries is back spawn.
<br />

<br />
Other than those few worries he's easy.  Proof is in the fact a guild on my server did him without using a single cleric in their raid  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_wall.gif" alt="Brick wall" border="0" /> .  Tho they did wipe at least once.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=741463" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.heartofsword.us/content/images/misc/azuth.gif" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
