			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Alduous, if I could make one suggestion-- work on spell casting mastery3.  I noticed you don't have it.  It is probably one of the most valuable AAs because you will be reducing the cost of spells you specialize in by 30% which allows you nuke much longer.  It actually makes much more sense to buy scm3 over mc3 because (for example):
<br />

<br />
Sun vortex- 390 mana
<br />
Sun vortex (with scm3)- 273 mana (117 mana saving)
<br />
Amount of time it would take to regen 117 mana that you saved with mc3-- 39 ticks / 3 min, 54 seconds
<br />

<br />
In short, get scm3-- you will appreciate it greatly.  =)<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.hneguild.com" target=_blank>Heaven and Earth</a>
<br />
Saryrn</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
