			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A very good way to get great gear is do a lot of hard ldon's or get into GoD sewer/mountain trials.
<br />

<br />
I've been pursuing this approach with my alt Hadewig, an enchanter, who cannot earn loot from raids (being an alt).
<br />

<br />
Some of the stuff I've won on randoms lately are :
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24894" target="_blank">http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24894</a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24000" target="_blank">http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24000</a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24177" target="_blank">http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24177</a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=23442" target="_blank">http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=23442</a>
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24743" target="_blank">http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=24743</a>
<br />

<br />
Last one is from the first Sewer trial:
<br />

<br />
<a href="http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=26402" target="_blank">http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=26402</a>
<br />

<br />
And there's loads of other nice stuff to get from these dungeons. Check this site <a href="http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/LDoN.aspx" target="_blank">http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/LDoN.aspx</a> and select 'drop' 'hard ldon' 'armor' and your preferred slot.
<br />

<br />
And of course with al your points you can buy ldon vendor armor/augments too. The Mistmoore armor is the best for casters (1451 points per item). I like the Hp20/mana 20 augments too which you can buy.
<br />

<br />
Get into those hard ldon groups m8. It's exciting and rewarding.<br />_________________<br />Belgicana 
<br />
65 Arch Convoker of Lowland Elites
<br />
Antonius Bayle
<br />

<br />
